      <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head> 
      <p>Includes instruction and user manuals, trade catalogs, and
        advertisements for cameras and other photographic equipment and supplies. Some
        were issued by Eastman Kodak.</p> 
    </scopecontent> 
